history.content:
This issue has been fixed and the wait lists limit for each secondary section has been increased.  

 Thanks for your patience.  Give it another go and contact me with any issues.

My Telebears Phase I is right now, and when I try to enroll in EE 16A, it prompts me to select a lab section -- but all of the lab sections are full, so I am unable to enroll in the class or even get on the waitlist. I am an EECS freshman with sophomore standing, so I thought I would be able to at least put myself on the waitlist. Why is Telebears doing this, and what should I do?
history.subject: Couldn't enroll in waitlist for EE 16A.
